    <h2>Kubernetes Orchestration Guide</h2>

    
    
    

    <p>Kubernetes orchestrates containerized applications across clusters of machines, providing automated deployment and scaling.</p>

    

    <h2>Pods</h2>

    
    

    <p>Pods are the smallest deployable units in Kubernetes. Each pod contains one or more containers that share storage and network resources.</p>

    <p><img src="https://example.com/images/pod-diagram.png" alt="Pod Architecture">
